It has been wiſely ſaid, that
the circulating medium being the ſoul and food of commerce, a corporation poſſeſſing a power of the ſoul can animate or annihilate the body at pleaſure;
if this miſerly monopolizing ſpirit is purſued, the body muſt indeed die a painful and lingering death and carry contagion and ruin into its courſe.
